\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tsf1665702712830_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tsf1665702712830_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tsf1665702712830_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tsf1665702712830\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Auto Jump\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether the cursor automatically jumps to the next field in the prompt sequence when the maximum field length is reached. The default is <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__section_w2695ab1b5b1_w2696ab1b5_w2697ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">JMP</code> field syntax code.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The next field in the prompt sequence automatically gets focus when the maximum number of characters has been reached.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tsf1665702712830__table_d11351e1_d11352e1_d11353e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The current field retains focus.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__section_ym2_31m_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1083508e130\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__p_d7970e1_d7971e1_d7972e1\">Auto jump is affected by the maximum field length, which\n            is counted in characters, not bytes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__p_d7973e1_d7974e1_d7975e1\">If incorrect data is entered in the field, the cursor\n            remains in the field until the data is correct, even if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Auto Jump</span>\n            is <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__section_i1k_j1m_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1083508e148\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__ul_k2m_k1m_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tsf1665702712830__li_d39941e1_d39942e1_d39943e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbr1665702712405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.\">Modeled Field Syntax</a> for Edit Box and Unifield widgets </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423330\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423330\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Auto Jump Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Auto Jump Specify whether the cursor automatically jumps to the next field in the prompt sequence when the maximum field length is reached. The default is False . Value Description True Sets the JMP field syntax code. The next field in the prompt sequence automatically gets focus when the maximum number of characters has been reached. False The current field retains focus. Description Auto jump is affected by the maximum field length, which is counted in characters, not bytes. If incorrect data is entered in the field, the cursor remains in the field until the data is correct, even if Auto Jump is True . Applies To Modeled Field Syntax for Edit Box and Unifield widgets Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}